```scss
.custom-appbar {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #108E91 0%, #20B6AA 100%);
  color: white;
}
```

### Primary Buttons
```scss
.btn-primary {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #108E91 0%, #20B6AA 100%);
  border: none;
  color: white;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(16, 142, 145, 0.3);

  &:hover {
